<TEXT>
LAST YEAR'S oilseeds dispute between the US and the EC cost Allied-Lyons,
the UK food and drinks group, between Dollars 2m and Dollars 3m (Pounds
1.3m-Pounds 1.96m) in lost profits, the company said yesterday, writes Peter
