</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
GOLD shares recovered after an early consolidation as the bullion price
edged back up towards Dollars 370 an ounce. The gold index shed 12 to 1,650,
after a low of 1,616. Industrials added 18 to 4,443 while the overall index
eased 13 to 3,891.
